title: DigitalPh33r (JonCJG)'s "It's a Wonderful Live"
description:
DigitalPh33r (now known as JonCJG)'s three episode machinima series - It's a Wonderful Live.


I'm a fan of Jon's machinima, so I decided to download them all in .avi format either through zamzar from youtube, or when it gave me this "target has size of 0 bytes" error, I would use the flashgot addon for firefox and convert to .avi with Pazera FLV to AVI convertor. I thought that there might be a chance that some other fans may want these videos as well, so I figured I would upload them for the lulz. If you're unsatisfied with the quality of the video I'd welcome suggestions on how to download them while keeping its original quality.


I will upload Hard Justice, It's a Wonderful Live, One Life Remaining, and Arby 'n' the Chief in their "seasons" as they are completed, and I get around to downloading them, in the event the reader would want those as well. I plan on using zamzar to download Roosterteeth's Halo Reach Fails of the Weak also. 

I'm a fan of machinima, but my horizons are limited, if anyone sees this and would like to recommend some lulzy machinima for my viewing pleasure, feel free to do so.


Love,
     
Jeddy
